Description:
    Generates a new Me Salva! customized model scaffold.
    Pass the model name as an argument, either CamelCased or snake_cased.
    It is possible to pass the attributes arguments as well.

Examples:
    `bin/rails generate ms_model_scaffold Awesome`
    `bin/rails generate ms_model_scaffold Awesome attribute1:string attribute2:integer attribute3:references`

    creates a Me Salva! customized awesome model scaffold:
        create the migration at db/migrate
        app/models/awesome.rb
        app/serializers/awesome_serializer.rb
        spec/models/awesome_spec.rb
        spec/factories/awesome_factory.rb
